Chapter 2: â€œThe Flippeningâ€
Keeping track of which cards have been flipped and which have found their soulmate was a bit like trying to remember where I left my keys. In a fit of what I can only describe as â€œcoding grace,â€ I managed to wrangle some state variables into submission.

